{"tid":1538474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府讓步，班白衫高層大SIR會出賣你地班前線警察 覺醒吧","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:57:02.000Z","uid":222970,"like":545,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"81d7419e4bf9ac877729af169e1e8121d8e2c5ae","tid":1538474,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"平時功勞就班白衫高層大sir拎<br />\n有鑊就你地班前線警察頂<br />\n相信你地都好明白依個道理<br />\n<br />\n所有開槍 私刑暴力鎮壓既警察好快會被清算<br />\n政府已經當你地condom用完即棄<br />\n好快就送你地上國際法庭<br />\n<br />\n你唔係以為呢三個月你地既惡行可以就咁算數？<br />\n<br />\n趁依家仲可以返轉頭 快d向告密督灰邊個大阿sir叫過你地做過d咩任務<br />\n<br />\n如果依家仲唔倒戈 你地被清算下場係會好慘"},{"pid":"c4f97a83249c6e27786047ac1567340a8f239d09","tid":1538474,"uid":287594,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"ab05feb7d0cb94faa603d1c371ae45a079d3de30","tid":1538474,"uid":259618,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"831 香港警察策謀恐襲<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"795a5e002c2671470b4c296ccd8da1958102eb74","tid":1538474,"uid":4075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月7 機場<br />\n9月8 美領</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"ba590d25364fd0e646bbaa9dbdfe98540064d8f1","tid":1538474,"uid":28970,"like":3